CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS "EventStoreRecord" ("id" TEXT NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY,"tenantId" TEXT,"stream" TEXT NOT NULL,"eventType" TEXT NOT NULL,"aggregateType" TEXT NOT NULL,"aggregateId" TEXT NOT NULL,"version" INTEGER NOT NULL DEFAULT 1,"payload" JSONB NOT NULL,"metadata" JSONB,"status" TEXT NOT NULL DEFAULT 'PENDING',"attempts" INTEGER NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,"replayedAt" TIMESTAMP(3),"deadLetterAt" TIMESTAMP(3),"createdAt" TIMESTAMP(3) NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP);
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS "MessageQueueRecord" ("id" TEXT NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY,"tenantId" TEXT,"provider" TEXT NOT NULL,"queueName" TEXT NOT NULL,"jobType" TEXT NOT NULL,"payload" JSONB NOT NULL,"status" TEXT NOT NULL DEFAULT 'PENDING',"priority" INTEGER NOT NULL DEFAULT 5,"attempts" INTEGER NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,"maxAttempts" INTEGER NOT NULL DEFAULT 5,"delayedUntil" TIMESTAMP(3),"lockedAt" TIMESTAMP(3),"processedAt" TIMESTAMP(3),"deadLetterAt" TIMESTAMP(3),"lastError" TEXT,"createdAt" TIMESTAMP(3) NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,"updatedAt" TIMESTAMP(3) NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP);
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS "SchedulerRecord" ("id" TEXT NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY,"tenantId" TEXT,"code" TEXT NOT NULL UNIQUE,"name" TEXT NOT NULL,"cron" TEXT,"calendar" JSONB,"jobType" TEXT NOT NULL,"payload" JSONB NOT NULL,"status" TEXT NOT NULL DEFAULT 'ACTIVE',"lastRunAt" TIMESTAMP(3),"nextRunAt" TIMESTAMP(3),"lastError" TEXT,"history" JSONB,"createdAt" TIMESTAMP(3) NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,"updatedAt" TIMESTAMP(3) NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP);
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS "NotificationPipelineRecord" ("id" TEXT NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY,"tenantId" TEXT,"channel" TEXT NOT NULL,"queueName" TEXT NOT NULL,"recipient" TEXT NOT NULL,"template" TEXT,"payload" JSONB NOT NULL,"status" TEXT NOT NULL DEFAULT 'PENDING',"attempts" INTEGER NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,"maxAttempts" INTEGER NOT NULL DEFAULT 5,"scheduledAt" TIMESTAMP(3) NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,"sentAt" TIMESTAMP(3),"failedAt" TIMESTAMP(3),"lastError" TEXT,"createdAt" TIMESTAMP(3) NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,"updatedAt" TIMESTAMP(3) NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP);
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS "AuditIntelligenceRecord" ("id" TEXT NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY,"tenantId" TEXT,"actorUserId" TEXT,"objectType" TEXT NOT NULL,"objectId" TEXT,"action" TEXT NOT NULL,"before" JSONB,"after" JSONB,"fieldDiff" JSONB,"ipAddress" TEXT,"deviceHash" TEXT,"riskScore" DOUBLE PRECISION NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,"metadata" JSONB,"createdAt" TIMESTAMP(3) NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP);
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS "InfrastructureConnector" ("id" TEXT NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY,"tenantId" TEXT,"provider" TEXT NOT NULL,"name" TEXT NOT NULL,"baseUrl" TEXT,"authType" TEXT NOT NULL,"config" JSONB NOT NULL,"secretCipher" TEXT,"status" TEXT NOT NULL DEFAULT 'DISCONNECTED',"lastSyncAt" TIMESTAMP(3),"lastError" TEXT,"createdAt" TIMESTAMP(3) NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,"updatedAt" TIMESTAMP(3) NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,UNIQUE("tenantId","provider","name"));
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS "AICopilotRecord" ("id" TEXT NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY,"tenantId" TEXT,"type" TEXT NOT NULL,"prompt" TEXT NOT NULL,"context" JSONB,"output" JSONB,"status" TEXT NOT NULL DEFAULT 'READY',"model" TEXT,"createdById" TEXT,"createdAt" TIMESTAMP(3) NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,"updatedAt" TIMESTAMP(3) NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP);
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS "DocumentAIRecord" ("id" TEXT NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY,"tenantId" TEXT,"type" TEXT NOT NULL,"fileUrl" TEXT NOT NULL,"language" TEXT,"status" TEXT NOT NULL DEFAULT 'PENDING',"extractedText" TEXT,"entities" JSONB,"confidence" DOUBLE PRECISION,"createdAt" TIMESTAMP(3) NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,"updatedAt" TIMESTAMP(3) NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP);
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS "BIEngineRecord" ("id" TEXT NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY,"tenantId" TEXT,"type" TEXT NOT NULL,"code" TEXT NOT NULL,"name" TEXT NOT NULL,"definition" JSONB NOT NULL,"result" JSONB,"status" TEXT NOT NULL DEFAULT 'ACTIVE',"createdAt" TIMESTAMP(3) NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,"updatedAt" TIMESTAMP(3) NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,UNIQUE("tenantId","type","code"));
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS "SecurityEnterpriseRecord" ("id" TEXT NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY,"tenantId" TEXT,"type" TEXT NOT NULL,"provider" TEXT,"name" TEXT NOT NULL,"config" JSONB NOT NULL,"status" TEXT NOT NULL DEFAULT 'ACTIVE',"riskScore" DOUBLE PRECISION NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,"createdAt" TIMESTAMP(3) NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,"updatedAt" TIMESTAMP(3) NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP);
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS "DevOpsCenterRecord" ("id" TEXT NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY,"tenantId" TEXT,"type" TEXT NOT NULL,"name" TEXT NOT NULL,"environment" TEXT,"config" JSONB NOT NULL,"status" TEXT NOT NULL DEFAULT 'ACTIVE',"createdAt" TIMESTAMP(3) NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,"updatedAt" TIMESTAMP(3) NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP);
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS "MonitoringEnterpriseRecord" ("id" TEXT NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY,"tenantId" TEXT,"type" TEXT NOT NULL,"source" TEXT NOT NULL,"metric" TEXT NOT NULL,"value" DOUBLE PRECISION NOT NULL,"unit" TEXT,"status" TEXT NOT NULL DEFAULT 'OK',"traceId" TEXT,"metadata" JSONB,"capturedAt" TIMESTAMP(3) NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP);
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS "DatabaseStudioRecord" ("id" TEXT NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY,"type" TEXT NOT NULL,"name" TEXT NOT NULL,"schemaName" TEXT,"artifact" JSONB NOT NULL,"status" TEXT NOT NULL DEFAULT 'ACTIVE',"createdAt" TIMESTAMP(3) NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,"updatedAt" TIMESTAMP(3) NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP);
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS "EnterpriseAdminRecord" ("id" TEXT NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY,"tenantId" TEXT,"type" TEXT NOT NULL,"name" TEXT NOT NULL,"plan" TEXT,"usage" JSONB,"billing" JSONB,"config" JSONB NOT NULL,"status" TEXT NOT NULL DEFAULT 'ACTIVE',"createdAt" TIMESTAMP(3) NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,"updatedAt" TIMESTAMP(3) NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP);
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS "WhiteLabelRecord" ("id" TEXT NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY,"tenantId" TEXT,"domain" TEXT UNIQUE,"logoUrl" TEXT,"theme" JSONB NOT NULL,"fonts" JSONB,"colors" JSONB,"emailBranding" JSONB,"loginBranding" JSONB,"isActive" BOOLEAN NOT NULL DEFAULT true,"createdAt" TIMESTAMP(3) NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,"updatedAt" TIMESTAMP(3) NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP);
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS "MarketplacePlugin" ("id" TEXT NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY,"code" TEXT NOT NULL UNIQUE,"name" TEXT NOT NULL,"version" TEXT NOT NULL,"description" TEXT,"manifest" JSONB NOT NULL,"dependencies" JSONB,"status" TEXT NOT NULL DEFAULT 'AVAILABLE',"installedAt" TIMESTAMP(3),"createdAt" TIMESTAMP(3) NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,"updatedAt" TIMESTAMP(3) NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP);
CREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS "EventStoreRecord_stream_idx" ON "EventStoreRecord"("stream"); CREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS "EventStoreRecord_eventType_idx" ON "EventStoreRecord"("eventType"); CREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS "EventStoreRecord_status_idx" ON "EventStoreRecord"("status");
CREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS "MessageQueueRecord_provider_idx" ON "MessageQueueRecord"("provider"); CREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS "MessageQueueRecord_queueName_idx" ON "MessageQueueRecord"("queueName"); CREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS "MessageQueueRecord_status_idx" ON "MessageQueueRecord"("status");
CREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS "SchedulerRecord_status_idx" ON "SchedulerRecord"("status"); CREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS "SchedulerRecord_nextRunAt_idx" ON "SchedulerRecord"("nextRunAt");
CREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS "NotificationPipelineRecord_channel_idx" ON "NotificationPipelineRecord"("channel"); CREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS "NotificationPipelineRecord_status_idx" ON "NotificationPipelineRecord"("status");
CREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS "AuditIntelligenceRecord_actorUserId_idx" ON "AuditIntelligenceRecord"("actorUserId"); CREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS "AuditIntelligenceRecord_objectType_objectId_idx" ON "AuditIntelligenceRecord"("objectType","objectId");
CREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS "InfrastructureConnector_provider_idx" ON "InfrastructureConnector"("provider"); CREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS "InfrastructureConnector_status_idx" ON "InfrastructureConnector"("status");
CREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS "AICopilotRecord_type_idx" ON "AICopilotRecord"("type"); CREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS "AICopilotRecord_status_idx" ON "AICopilotRecord"("status");
CREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS "DocumentAIRecord_type_idx" ON "DocumentAIRecord"("type"); CREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS "DocumentAIRecord_status_idx" ON "DocumentAIRecord"("status");
CREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS "BIEngineRecord_type_idx" ON "BIEngineRecord"("type"); CREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS "BIEngineRecord_status_idx" ON "BIEngineRecord"("status");
CREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS "SecurityEnterpriseRecord_type_idx" ON "SecurityEnterpriseRecord"("type"); CREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS "SecurityEnterpriseRecord_provider_idx" ON "SecurityEnterpriseRecord"("provider");
CREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS "DevOpsCenterRecord_type_idx" ON "DevOpsCenterRecord"("type"); CREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS "DevOpsCenterRecord_environment_idx" ON "DevOpsCenterRecord"("environment");
CREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS "MonitoringEnterpriseRecord_type_idx" ON "MonitoringEnterpriseRecord"("type"); CREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS "MonitoringEnterpriseRecord_status_idx" ON "MonitoringEnterpriseRecord"("status");
CREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS "DatabaseStudioRecord_type_idx" ON "DatabaseStudioRecord"("type"); CREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS "EnterpriseAdminRecord_type_idx" ON "EnterpriseAdminRecord"("type"); CREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS "WhiteLabelRecord_isActive_idx" ON "WhiteLabelRecord"("isActive"); CREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS "MarketplacePlugin_status_idx" ON "MarketplacePlugin"("status");
